		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">32.106</ph> Order of preference.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">The contracting officer must consider the following order of preference when a contractor requests contract financing, unless an exception would be in the Governmentâ€™s best interest in a specific case:</p>
			      <ol id="d2022e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2036e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Private financing without Government guarantee. It is not intended, however, that the contracting officer require the contractor to obtain private financing-</p>
					          <ol id="d2022e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2036e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                At unreasonable terms; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2036e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                From other agencies.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2036e50" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Customary contract financing other than loan guarantees and certain advance payments (see <xref href="FAR-i1083846.dita#i1083846"
                        base="i1083846"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.113</xref>).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2036e62" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Loan guarantees.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2036e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Unusual contract financing (see <xref href="FAR-i1083893.dita#i1083893"
                        base="i1083893"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.114</xref>).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2036e83" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Advance payments (see exceptions in <xref href="FAR-i1082582.dita#i1082582"
                        base="i1082582"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.402</xref>(b)).</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
